{"tid":2410228,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"深圳教育局擬招聘港澳教師 建立大灣區特色職業教育園區","createTime":"2021-02-16T12:12:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T12:30:24.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"73d3fbd234931fb313f95c1b4d9c9898afc7de68","tid":2410228,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T12:12:03.000Z","msg":"深圳市教育局本月10日在官網發佈《深圳市教育局2021年工作要點》（下稱《文件》）指，在學生交流、師資方面，提出更多深港融合的方案，包括計劃改良大學教師招聘制度，招聘合資格的港澳籍人士，並鼓勵他們參與教師資格認定，及建立大灣區教育園區等。<br />\n<br />\n師資融合方面，《文件》指「優化教師招聘制度，推進符合條件的港澳籍人士參加教師資格認定和參與教師招聘」；《文件》第10項「啟動實施國家職業教育創新發展高地建設工程」中，指深圳職業教育重視訊息職業技術學院，將建立職業教育微電子人才培養示範基地，加快推進產教融合型企業培育、示範性特色產業學院建設，推動建立粵港澳大灣區特色職業教育園區及加快建立深汕職業教育園區。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210216/44FIUHEQ5NGCLD4M3NRDMRGCZA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210216%2F44FIUHEQ5NGCLD4M3NRDMRGCZA%2F&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BQ0QAWntaMGUWBfwPSaCbl8%3D&h=742735d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210216%2F44FIUHEQ5NGCLD4M3NRDMRGCZA%2F&h=997b58c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210216/44FIUHEQ5NGCLD4M3NRDMRGCZA/</a>"},{"pid":"68392d596b456bc8dcf0e4fb9518e81f839c88b8","tid":2410228,"uid":71279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T12:17:23.000Z","msg":"大陸人落嚟搶教席<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a5b713841331f9c1b520edfcd778031517630d","tid":2410228,"uid":38528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T12:18:28.000Z","msg":"人工冇100k唔會有人上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"460a411554a5f7c6324b8d7a53b3c45fe0860f57","tid":2410228,"uid":31017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T12:22:42.000Z","msg":"騰籠換鳥<br />\n將香港人趕上去做老師<br />\n支那人落嚟教愛黨愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm